casebody.data:
Monday, January 6, 1997

MOTION DOCKET

96-2790. State v. Clemons.

Hamilton C.P. No. B9511119. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Common Pleas of Hamilton County. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of execution.

IT IS ORDERED by the court that a stay of execution be, and hereby is, granted, pending further order of this court.

Douglas, J., would grant pending this court’s decision on direct appeal. Pfeifer, J., would grant to a time certain.
